  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Our protagonist once dreamed of becoming a comic artist.<br>But over time, he begins to lose confidence in that dream.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As high school graduation approaches, he finds himself spending the summer break at school<br>where he meets <strong>two girls</strong>, Han Yerin and Lee Seohyun.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3841730/extras/ef080e7a922d038620c43edb967f68b7.avif?t=1773970352\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A restless youth, uncertain about the future...<br>What kind of experiences await him through these encounters?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Over 10 hours of gameplay</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A visual novel with stylish and emotional presentation</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fully voiced main characters (2 heroines) with original vocal tracks</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Collectible elements and a light character growth system</strong></p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Our protagonist once dreamed of becoming a comic artist.<br>But over time, he begins to lose confidence in that dream.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As high school graduation approaches, he finds himself spending the summer break at school<br>where he meets <strong>two girls</strong>, Han Yerin and Lee Seohyun.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3841730/extras/ef080e7a922d038620c43edb967f68b7.avif?t=1773970352\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A restless youth, uncertain about the future...<br>What kind of experiences await him through these encounters?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Over 10 hours of gameplay</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A visual novel with stylish and emotional presentation</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fully voiced main characters (2 heroines) with original vocal tracks</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Collectible elements and a light character growth system</strong></p></li></ul>",
